reviewText: This dvd is awesome for a action fan of movies i reccomened this dvd
Good bargain but get it with this in mind.  You are buying Terminator, a great classic, and getting Robocop for free.
Both movies are amazing! I love these cyborg films! They both come with great action, plot, acting, special effects! Buy it now! Or you will never forgive yourself!!!!

(I meant 4 stars, not 2. Oops) If you grew up in the 1980's like me, than this particular Double Feature Editon should seem very savory. Although 2 very different films thematically, both Terminator and Robocop deal with very cool cyborg stories. I remember loving both these films as a kid and the concept of having both these films on one package is a no brainer, especially if you don't have these in your DVD library already. Bottom line, you won't get more wall-to-wall cyborg action in one package than this beauty!
